Interface DiscreteUncertainObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FeatureVector<java.lang.Double>, SpatialComparable, UncertainObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UnweightedDiscreteUncertainObject, WeightedDiscreteUncertainObject
    public interface DiscreteUncertainObject
extends UncertainObject
    Interface for discrete uncertain objects, that are represented by a finite (possibly weighted) number of samples.
